{"word":"ἀποδάκνω","slug":"ἀποδάκνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀποδάκνω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to bite off a piece of</i> a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>μῆλα ἀποδεδηγμένα</el> <i>with pieces bitten out</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to bite hard, gnaw</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}